review: (Translated by Google) It could have been a 4-star, but it was reduced because of the service that was not so deft. The cooking is good, the price is standard. Besides ala carte, there is also a package menu per 4 people (65-69 thousand per person). The difference in this package menu is that crabs are no longer counted in ounces, but have already been included in the price of the package. Price per ounce (01/26/2020) 32.5 thousand. In addition to the crab menu here also provides shrimp, squid, fish and chicken. Krabe is a group with the adjacent Super Penyet. (Original) Seharusnya dapat bintang 4, tapi dikurangi karena pelayanannya yang kurang cekatan. Masakannya enak, harganya standar. Untuk hitungan menu kepiting ala carte dihitung dari harga pasar per ons. 1 porsi isi 1 ekor sekitar 3,8 - 4,5 ons. Selain ala carte juga tersedia menu paketan per 4 orang (per orang dikenai 65-69 ribu). Bedanya di menu paket ini kepitingnya tidak lagi dihitung per ons, tapi sudah masuk ke dalam harga paketnya. Harga per ons (01/26/2020) 32,5 ribu. Selain menu kepiting disini juga menyediakan udang, cumi, ikan dan ayam. Krabe ini satu grup dengan Super Penyet yang bersebelahan.
